{"books":[{"id":"CCRD-fanyou","name":"中国反右运动数据库","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":[""],"article":{"title":"大字报诗三首","authors":["刘奇弟","北京大学"],"dates":[{"year":1957,"month":5,"day":20}],"is_range_date":false,"parts":[{"text":"大字报诗三首","type":"title"},{"text":"北京大学刘奇弟","type":"authors"},{"text":"（刘奇弟：北京大学物理系学生）","type":"subtitle"},{"text":"(一)是时候了","type":"subtitle"},{"text":"我不害怕做傻瓜","type":"paragraph"},{"text":"我要重复别人的话","type":"paragraph"},{"text":"而且还要高唱","type":"paragraph"},{"text":"是时候了","type":"paragraph"},{"text":"是时候了","type":"paragraph"},{"text":"为何不是时候？","type":"paragraph"},{"text":"难道谁还苦闷得不够？","type":"paragraph"},{"text":"为何不是时候？","type":"paragraph"},{"text":"我们的嘴还要封多久？","type":"paragraph"},{"text":"为何不是时候？","type":"paragraph"},{"text":"你还想着千万人头落地？","type":"paragraph"},{"text":"(斯大林杀的忠诚党员)","type":"paragraph"},{"text":"为何不是时候？","type":"paragraph"},{"text":"你还要等匈牙利事件再起？","type":"paragraph"},{"text":"(拉科西种的根)","type":"paragraph"},{"text":"老兄！","type":"paragraph"},{"text":"是时候了！","type":"paragraph"},{"text":"是时候了！！","type":"paragraph"},{"text":"(二)献给沈、张二君(〈是时候了〉的原著者)","type":"subtitle"},{"text":"听！","type":"paragraph"},{"text":"这声音多了亮，","type":"paragraph"},{"text":"它！","type":"paragraph"},{"text":"震撼心灵。","type":"paragraph"},{"text":"它！","type":"paragraph"},{"text":"充满着痛苦","type":"paragraph"},{"text":"它！","type":"paragraph"},{"text":"洋溢着爱情。","type":"paragraph"},{"text":"但是","type":"paragraph"},{"text":"有人想要堵住它，","type":"paragraph"},{"text":"可不是他害怕。","type":"paragraph"},{"text":"哈哈！","type":"paragraph"},{"text":"你越害怕","type":"paragraph"},{"text":"越想堵它","type":"paragraph"},{"text":"这声音越要响得大。","type":"paragraph"},{"text":"看！","type":"paragraph"},{"text":"这火炬多明亮","type":"paragraph"},{"text":"它！","type":"paragraph"},{"text":"照亮眼睛","type":"paragraph"},{"text":"它！","type":"paragraph"},{"text":"驱散黑暗","type":"paragraph"},{"text":"它！","type":"paragraph"},{"text":"确是来自“五四”之光","type":"paragraph"},{"text":"但是","type":"paragraph"},{"text":"有人想要熄灭它。","type":"paragraph"},{"text":"可不是他害怕","type":"paragraph"},{"text":"哈哈！","type":"paragraph"},{"text":"你还没熄灭那儿的。","type":"paragraph"},{"text":"我这里又点起来哪！","type":"paragraph"},{"text":"(三)白毛女伸冤","type":"subtitle"},{"text":"(有人批评〈是时候了〉说","type":"paragraph"},{"text":"它的基调彷彿是白毛女伸冤)","type":"paragraph"},{"text":"我有冤来我有仇","type":"paragraph"},{"text":"我的冤仇说不完(尤其是大字报)","type":"paragraph"},{"text":"(1)","type":"paragraph"},{"text":"二年前(55年)","type":"paragraph"},{"text":"祸从天降下，","type":"paragraph"},{"text":"无缘无故","type":"paragraph"},{"text":"被糟塌","type":"paragraph"},{"text":"张三瞅着耳朵嚷！","type":"paragraph"},{"text":"李四指着鼻子骂！","type":"paragraph"},{"text":"“反党(一)反人民(一)反革命”","type":"paragraph"},{"text":"啊！天知道","type":"paragraph"},{"text":"白毛女","type":"paragraph"},{"text":"“反党，反人民，反革命”！","type":"paragraph"},{"text":"要问白毛女是谁，","type":"paragraph"},{"text":"——北大二百多被斗者。","type":"paragraph"},{"text":"(极少数的反革命除外)。","type":"paragraph"},{"text":"白毛女今天要问","type":"paragraph"},{"text":"我怎么是","type":"paragraph"},{"text":"“反党，反人民，反革命”？","type":"paragraph"},{"text":"(2)","type":"paragraph"},{"text":"——谁都知道","type":"paragraph"},{"text":"24斋是宿舍","type":"paragraph"},{"text":"却很少人知","type":"paragraph"},{"text":"它代替过牢狱，","type":"paragraph"},{"text":"个个房间","type":"paragraph"},{"text":"由积极分子看管，","type":"paragraph"},{"text":"走道两头，","type":"paragraph"},{"text":"有校卫队把守","type":"paragraph"},{"text":"夜里捆着睡","type":"paragraph"},{"text":"白天一步也不准走","type":"paragraph"},{"text":"白毛女","type":"paragraph"},{"text":"在那里","type":"paragraph"},{"text":"天哪","type":"paragraph"},{"text":"“反省”","type":"paragraph"},{"text":"“反省”","type":"paragraph"},{"text":"白毛女是谁","type":"paragraph"},{"text":"——几十个被禁的北大人(除个别的反革命分子)的化身。","type":"paragraph"},{"text":"今天，","type":"paragraph"},{"text":"白毛女要问","type":"paragraph"},{"text":"逮捕证在那里？","type":"paragraph"},{"text":"为什么","type":"paragraph"},{"text":"私设公堂","type":"paragraph"},{"text":"私人审讯","type":"paragraph"},{"text":"为什么","type":"paragraph"},{"text":"伤害人身心？","type":"paragraph"},{"text":"宪法做什么用？","type":"paragraph"},{"text":"这谁想出的主意！","type":"paragraph"},{"text":"是谁？","type":"paragraph"},{"text":"是谁？","type":"paragraph"},{"text":"怎么？","type":"paragraph"},{"text":"是群众？","type":"paragraph"},{"text":"这个","type":"paragraph"},{"text":"就算我相信","type":"paragraph"},{"text":"但是","type":"paragraph"},{"text":"你们(当时掌……的人)","type":"paragraph"},{"text":"都效忠于","type":"paragraph"},{"text":"无政府主义？？","type":"paragraph"},{"text":"同学们","type":"paragraph"},{"text":"你们公平，公评","type":"paragraph"},{"text":"这是不是冤？","type":"paragraph"},{"text":"要不要申？","type":"paragraph"},{"text":" 物三  刘奇弟  28斋452号  5月20日","type":"paragraph"},{"text":" 来源：北京大学社会主义思想教育委员会编印《北京大学右派分子反动言论汇集》，一九五七年十月。","type":"paragraph"}],"comments":[],"origin":"","comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":0,"page_end":0,"alias":""},"tags":[{"type":"文稿类型","name":"文章"}]}]}